        <li><strong>Smeg Enamel Finish Colors</strong> — Smeg's colored appliances use a high-temperature vitreous enamel coating — the same type of finish used on traditional Italian ceramic cookware. Enamel chips at sharp impact and cannot be touched up without full panel respray. Service requires non-abrasive tools, protective covers, and enamel-safe cleaning agents throughout. A chip on a Pastel Blue FAB28 is immediately visible and irreparable without specialist respray.</li>
